cs.DC, cs.NI, cs.PF, cs.AR, cs.SE 

The paper focuses on analyzing the performance of internode communication on large-scale systems, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and networked systems (cs.NI). The use of MPI_Send and the analysis of the I/O subsystem and network components suggest a focus on parallel and distributed computing (cs.PF) and architecture (cs.AR). The paper also discusses optimization efforts, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE).
